┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│         VFS (Virtual Layer)             │
│  - Path resolution (/dev/console)       │
│  - open/read/write/close                │
│  - Mount management                     │
└────────────┬───────────┬────────────────┘
             │           │
    ┌────────▼──────┐   ┌▼──────────────┐
    │    TmpFS      │   │    DevFS      │
    │  (RAM only)   │   │  (Devices)    │
    │               │   │               │
    │  Uses klime   │   │  Uses module  │
    │  for storage  │   │  system       │
    └───────────────┘   └───────────────┘
         ↓                    ↓
    /tmp/file.txt      /dev/console
    /var/log/boot      /dev/keyboard


system apps have a installer and cause their in the system the kernel installs everything needed for it itself
while external apps can/need to have one too but the user needs to run the script itself
